short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Format JSON in a modern way. With guaranteed order of keys, big numbers, jq queries, expandable/collapsable properties and more.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
KEY FEATURES:
- Fast parse and format JSON
- Supports big numbers (includes x64 integer and float)
- Guaranteed order of keys
- JQ expression support
- Formatted and Raw view switcher
- Array and Object expand/collapse
- Safe for selecting and copying JSON
- Clickable links
